---
title: Warm Salmon Poke Bowls with Radish Slaw and Sriracha Mayo
description: We're making some changes to a beloved bowl style and upping the heat (just a little!) to create a warm version. This dish features all the fresh elements of the poke bowl, along with the additions of tasty salmon and charred corn.
